reviewtext: I have had this keyboard for years now.  I really do not use the "internet" keys, but i really like the calculator key, seeing how im always looking to do a quick calculation.It might not be as quite as other keyboards, but the keys feel fine to push, and after years they have not broke or got stikky, and i have used it alot Daily.The arm rest is the best feature, along with the Huge spacebar.  The keys feel very natural, and i like how they slope up.  Well worth the money.~hope this helps
